text: KOWZ (100.9 FM) is a radio station licensed to Blooming Prairie, Minnesota and serving the Owatonna-Waseca/Minneapolis-St. Paul area. KOWZ carries a full service adult contemporary format. KOWZ (pronounced as "cows") is owned by Linder Radio Group, which owns radio stations in Owatonna, Mankato, St. James, and Marshall ==External links== *KOWZ official website Category:Radio stations in Minnesota Category:Adult contemporary radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 1996 Category:1996 establishments in Minnesota
